TextNode.WstringData: SPAWN POINT NOT SELECTED, PLEASE SELECT ONE
Warning! You are leaving the combat area! Desserters will be shot!

1) This is the MINIMAP. It shows the postions of both unattended vehicles (grey) as well as all of your teammates (blue/red). Press N to cycle through its zoom. Press M to bring it up a full-screen version. 2) This area displays icons for a number of different objects including Control Points, Ammo sources, and Medical lockers. If you see the icon you are close enough to benefit from that object. 3) This shows how many clips you have and the number of bullets in the loaded clip. Find an AMMO source to stock up on clips. 4) This icon shows if you are standing, crouching or prone. 5) This is your current health. Call a medic or find a Medical Locker to heal yourself. 6) This is your communication interface. Use it to coordinate with your teammates.
